For this plugin to work, you need to install (just copy) WIRIS filter into your Moodle filter folder.

Please extract it from the attached zip file and copy it to the filters folder in your Moodle's root folder
Then, navigate your browser to the main Admin block and press Notifications to install and enable the
WIRIS CAS and Formula plugins.

Then, Enable the plugin in the Appearance >> HTMLAREA Custom plugins settings page.